name: DIVINITY #000
description:
Pure piece created using CLIP Guided Diffusion.

Humanity in this world is very closed to many different gods.

Some of them are merciful, others gruesome, twisted and bloodthirsty.

The way for the believer to reach their gods are through the "god stone" not through prayers or supplications.

This world belongs to us, it's up to you to decide which god is linked to this stone.
